<p>
  <span class="nym">Idony</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old Icelandic</span> <i>Iðunn</i>, the name of a goddess associated with apples and youth.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>The Latinization <i>Idonea</i> was influenced by <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>idoneus, idonea</i> 'suitable, fit, proper'.</p>
</div>
  


<dl>
<dt><span class="area">England</span></dt>
<dd>
<dl>
